   delineate a new organizational framework for doing business in emerging
   markets and for optimizing gains from emerging market innovations. This
   Special Issue defines and clearly differentiates emerging market
   innovations (EMIs) from developed market innovations (DMIs) and provides
   a generalizable framework. The proposed framework corresponds to the
