   both stock market data and individual-level experimental data to show
   the effect of home-name effect on investors' behavior and stock market
   performance. Using stock trading records, Study 1 shows that home-name
   stocks significantly outperform non-home-name stocks in emerging Chinese
   stock markets dominated by retail investors. We replicate this home-name
