   attached consumers, products positioned via passionate love are more
   appealing to avoidant consumers, and anxious and fearful consumers find
   both equally appealing. Consistent with the notion of consumer-based
   strategy, we discuss how managers can leverage these insights in their
   segmentation, targeting, and positioning.
