   more positive affect, compared to the indirect RBs condition. Second, we
   document the process underlying each effect. The beneficial effect of
   direct RBs is explained by justice restoration, while the deleterious
   effect of indirect RBs is mainly explained by public exposure. Third, on
   the basis of our findings, we test different managerial tactics to
   reduce avengers' post desire for revenge. For direct avengers,
