   negative responses because these customers are primarily driven by
   justice restoration. For indirect avengers, our prescription involves
   taking initiatives to change their focus from public exposure to justice
   restoration by using proactive social media tools. This switch makes
   these latter customers more amenable to most recoveries, even poor ones.
