   possibility that the consumer can still use the promotional offer, so it
   emerges only for potential customers and existing customers of
   frequently bought products. Companies can mitigate the dark side of ex
   post extensions proactively, by designing the extensions to last for
   only a short time or offering an explanation for the extension that
   highlights the popularity of the initial promotion.
