AB A new product's success in the marketplace largely depends on salesforce
   actions. Many B2B salespeople display conservatism when confronted with
   new products in their portfolio, such that they maximize their efforts
   to sell existing products before engaging in efforts to sell the new
   product. So far, it is unclear whether this conservative selling
