   updates or an explanation may limit increases in compensation
   expectations over time. Still, their joint usage creates a
   "too-much-of-a-good-thing" effect, suggesting that if the usage of
   communication initiatives is taken too far it may lead to negative
   outcomes such as increasing compensation expectations.
