   experience management (CEM) as one of the most promising marketing
   approaches in consumer industries. In research, however, the notion of
   CEM is not well understood, is fragmented across a variety of contexts,
   and is insufficiently demarcated from other marketing management
   concepts. By integrating field-based insights of 52 managers engaging in
